=== 電氣特性 ===
游戏端口的輸出功率約可提供負載到 750 mA 的電流<ref name="rm-d1170">{{cite web|title=System board D1170 reference manual|url=http://www.rm.com/_RMVirtual/Media/Downloads/d1170.pdf|access-date=2010-04-15|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924091527/http://www.rm.com/_RMVirtual/Media/Downloads/d1170.pdf|dead-url=no}} 091205 rm.com</ref>，不過這是與其它的設備一起計算的，包含[[键盘_(输入设备)|鍵盤]]（最大 100 mA<ref name="img_custompublish_com-AK-4400-GP_Datasheet_pdf_return_www_tftplaza">{{cite web|title=Small footprint Notebook style PS/2 Keyboard|url=http://img.custompublish.com/getfile.php/628305.31.tbtabqqeba/AK-4400-GP_Datasheet.pdf?return=www.tftplaza.nl|access-date=2010-04-15|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128050541/http://img.custompublish.com/getfile.php/628305.31.tbtabqqeba/AK-4400-GP_Datasheet.pdf?return=www.tftplaza.nl|dead-url=no}} 091205 img.custompublish.com</ref>），[[鼠标|鼠标]]（約 25 mA<ref name="iammp-h2000">{{cite web|title=Solid-state optical mouse sensor with PS/2 and quadrature outputs. Technical Data. HDNS-2000|url=http://www.iammp.org/design/files/h2000.pdf|access-date=2010-04-15|archive-date=2018-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127180723/http://www.iammp.org/design/files/h2000.pdf|dead-url=no}} 091205 iammp.org</ref>），與視訊端口（[[视频图形阵列|VGA]]，使用 50 mA<ref name="rm-d1170" />），因此游戏端口實際能夠使用不到 575 mA。

